data.description: PRICE REDUCED!!!!Convenience and Comfort await! This beautiful 3 bed 2.5 bath home in Easley SC is ready for you! As you pull up you'll notice the curb appeal. An attractive and timeless brick facade blended perfectly with warm neutral color vinyl siding and classic black shutters. Step underneath the covered front porch and through the front door to find an inviting foyer with a spacious formal dining room to the right framed by a decorative archway. Plenty of space for a large table so the holiday gatherings can happen at your house! From the foyer you will cross underneath another decorative arch which leads to the heart of the home .... a large family room with a gas log fireplace surrounded by built-in shelves and cabinets on each side. This will work nicely to hold your favorite books and pictures of your loved ones so you will feel the the warmth, tranquility, and peace as you snuggle by the fire in your PJ's on Christmas eve waiting for Santa to fill your stocking which you've hung from your classy, clean white mantle piece! This home boasts an open floor plan which is perfect for entertaining. The living room spills into the kitchen and also spills into the backyard where you will LOVE the 16x16 covered patio with ceiling fan. This is a dream for outdoor entertaining! Imagine watching your favorite team play as you lounge on your wicker patio set and smell something tasty cooking in your big green egg.. ahhh... relaxation! Soak it in while it lasts because  the kids are certainly going to want to run around, scream, and play in this BIG backyard which is fully fenced in. The property actually runs well beyond the back fence as this is one of the largest lots in the neighborhood. Back inside the house you'll adore the tons of windows which let in ample sunlight. The vibe is warm, inviting, and pleasant! The kitchen boasts plenty of cabinetry and a nice sized island in the center which will certainly be the hub as you laugh and chat with your guests. Double closets in the kitchen provide bunches of pantry and storage space. There is also a nice sized laundry room and a half bath off the side of the kitchen. In between the kitchen and living room is the perfect amount of space for an eat-in kitchen. Pick your favorite round or square table! This is where the cereal will be shoveled in before running out the doors in the morning. Upstairs you will find a huge master suite offering two walk-in closets, separate vanities, a stand alone shower and separate garden tub. There are an additional 2 bedrooms and another full bath upstairs. The bedrooms are a great size. Your family will be very comfortable AND each bedroom boasts a walk-in closet. That's rare! BUT WAIT! There's more! A bonus room!!! This home offers a bonus room which could be used as an office, playroom, or  4th bedroom. What more do you need?! This home is conveniently located in the thriving town of Easley which is a short commute to Greenville, Anderson, and Clemson. Only minutes away from shopping, restaurants, and healthcare. This location is a major win! Don't miss your opportunity to make this home your own! Schedule a showing today!
